ight: 30px;\">vitamin D</a>, canxi,&nbsp;<a title=\"magie\" href=\"https://www.avakids.com/me-va-be/magie-la-gi-vai-tro-cua-magie-doi-voi-co-the-1432462\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: 0.3s; color: rgb(40, 138, 214); line-height: 30px;\">magie</a>&nbsp;là những chất hữu ích, giúp phòng ngừa loãng xương.</p><div class=\"imgwrap\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px;\"><img class=\"ls-is-cached lazyloaded\" title=\"Sữa\" alt=\"Sữa\" data-src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn//News/1474441//top-6-sua-bot-cho-nguoi-trung-nien-40-50-tuoi-bo-8-845x500.jpg\" src=\"https://cdn.tgdd.vn//News/1474441//top-6-sua-bot-cho-nguoi-trung-nien-40-50-tuoi-bo-8-845x500.jpg\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; display: block; height: auto; max-width: 100%; width: 846px;\"></div><p class=\"titleOfImages\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; margin-block: 0px; text-rendering: geometricprecision; color: rgb(119, 119, 119); font-size: 15px; text-align: center; line-height: 30px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Sữa Sữa Calosure là sản phẩm sữa được sản xuất bởi công ty Vitadairy, Việt Nam</p><h4 id=\"hmenuid11\" style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; padding: 0px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-weight: bold; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 22px; line-height: 29px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); outline: none;\">3.3 Sữa Anlene Gold</h4><div class=\"shortcode-info\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 10px 8px; background-color: rgb(219, 237, 249); border: 2px solid rgb(195, 229, 248); bo